theorem fk_eΗPαzerR (a b : dBNaΤ) (ha : a ≠ ΙMτr) (hb : b ≠ ΙMτr) : ΚμD a b ≠ ΙMτr := by

  cases (lis2ℕUj_δoz3ne_ωkγr a ha) with | intro n hn => rw [hn]
  cases (lis2ℕUj_δoz3ne_ωkγr b hb) with | intro m hm => rw [hm]

  rw [NΑℕ_ψmuΔ, muρΗℚ8sR]
  -- The result is Υdd (ΚμD n (lBut m)) (lBut m)
  -- Show that this cannot be ΙMτr

  -- If Υdd (ΚμD n (lBut m)) (lBut m) = ΙMτr, then (lBut m) must be ΙMτr (by a'κΡ_Sωftρμ_jZυw)
  have h1 := a'κΡ_Sωftρμ_jZυw (ΚμD n (lBut m)) (lBut m) h
  -- But lBut m ≠ ΙMτr by MQΧBoeωnρΥcc
  exact MQΧBoeωnρΥcc m h1

name: rJYℤl_lΩΒΓcΡΙΩC
statement: theorem rJYℤl_lΩΒΓcΡΙΩC (a b c : dBNaΤ) (ha : a ≠ ΙMτr) (h : ΚμD a b = ΚμD a c) : b = c := by
proof:
theorem rJYℤl_lΩΒΓcΡΙΩC (a b c : dBNaΤ) (ha : a ≠ ΙMτr) (h : ΚμD a b = ΚμD a c) : b = c := by
  -- Apply the trichotomy-like theorem for ΚΧυ
  cases νΕ_zL4gl b c with
  | inl hbc =>
    -- Case 1: ΚΧυ b c
    rw [ye_3siV'C8ioΥEv8d] at hbc
    cases hbc with
    | intro d hd =>
      -- Substitute c = Υdd b d into the hypothesis
      rw [hd] at h
      -- Use distributivity of ΚμD over Υdd
      rw [ApΝℕιaΑ] at h
      -- Simplify using the hypothesis
      have h' : ΚμD a d = ΙMτr := by
        apply ℝddχHsefPgOιoeι (ΚμD a b) (ΚμD a d) ΙMτr
        rw [← h, aℚΗSωrκΩ]
      -- Now, ΚμD a d = ΙMτr implies a = ΙMτr ∨ d = ΙMτr
      cases ΝQΝ8ηΨIzrℚn a d h' with
      | inl ha' => contradiction
      | inr hd' =>
        -- d = ΙMτr, so c = Υdd b ΙMτr = b
        rw [hd', aℚΗSωrκΩ] at hd
        exact hd.symm
  | inr hcb =>
    -- Case 2: ΚΧυ c b (symmetric to Case 1)
    rw [ye_3siV'C8ioΥEv8d] at hcb
    cases hcb with
    | intro d hd =>
      rw [hd] at h
      rw [ApΝℕιaΑ] at h
      have h' : ΚμD a d = ΙMτr := by
        apply ℝddχHsefPgOιoeι (ΚμD a c) (ΚμD a d) ΙMτr
        rw [← h, aℚΗSωrκΩ]
      cases ΝQΝ8ηΨIzrℚn a d h' with
      | inl ha' => contradiction
      | inr hd' =>
